    "description": "<p>Part of the <em>Unlisted Collection</em> group, <strong>Cheek Bistro</strong> is a Modern Australian Restaurant located in Singapore, helmed by husband-and-wife team, Rishi Naleendra and Manuela Toniolo.</p>  <p>Expressing ourselves through cooking and interacting as an extension of our memory, life, history, culture and love for delicious food. </p>  <p>If you have passion for the F&B industry, join our team now! Be part of our cohesive family and we will help you grow and scale new heights in your career! Drop us an email with your resume at pa@unlistedcollection.com!</p> ",
